            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>There is no systematic declassification of government documents in Sri Lanka.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>Mnistry of Foreign Affairs: Republic Building, Colombo 01</p>
                <p>Department of National Archives: P.O. Box 1414, No. 7, Reid Avenue, Colomobo 7.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head>Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers should write directly to the Ministry of Foreign Affairs to request
                    access to diplomatic documents.</p>
            </div>
